QuestData.Title: Spellbound
QuestData.Description: Grand Magister Rommath has something in his possession that I want.$b$bHe brought a very powerful tome with him. It would be better for our cause if it were no longer in Sunreaver hands.$b$bLocate Rommath's book of incantations and bring it to me.
QuestData.LogDescription: Retrieve Rommath's Book of Incantations from Dawnseeker Promontory.
